Description:
  Generate a skeleton for a mirrOS_api widget

Example:
  rails generate widget NAME
  rails generate widget NAME field_1:type field_2:type

  Available types:
    string
    integer
    float

This will create:
  widgets/NAME
  widgets/NAME/Rakefile
  widgets/NAME/README.md
  widgets/NAME/MIT-LICENSE
  widgets/NAME/NAME.gemspec
  widgets/NAME/Gemfile
  widgets/NAME/app/assets/templates/settings.vue
  widgets/NAME/app/controllers/NAME/application_controller.rb (optional)
  widgets/NAME/app/jobs/NAME/application_job.rb (optional)
  widgets/NAME/app/mailers/NAME/application_mailer.rb (optional)
  widgets/NAME/app/models/NAME/application_record.rb
  widgets/NAME/app/models/NAME/NAME_data.rb
  widgets/NAME/bin/rails
  widgets/NAME/config/routes.rb
  widgets/NAME/lib/NAME.rb
  widgets/NAME/lib/name/version.rb
  widgets/NAME/lib/name/engine.rb
  widgets/NAME/lib/name/fetcher.rb
  widgets/NAME/lib/tasks/NAME_tasks.rake (optional)
  widgets/NAME/test/...
